import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"
import { Switch, Router, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

import Splash from "/home/ubuntu/dev/src/pages/splash/Splash.js"
import Access from "/home/ubuntu/dev/src/pages/access/js/Access.js"
import Frontpage from "/home/ubuntu/dev/src/pages/frontpage/js/Frontpage.js"

import history from "/home/ubuntu/dev/src/js/history.js"
import CheckCookie from "./checkCookie"
import Authenticated from "./Authenticated"

export default function CustomRoutes() {

  const [loggedIn, setLoggedIn] = useState( false )

  return (
    <Router history={history}>
      <Switch>
        <Unauthenticated path="/" loggedIn={loggedIn} />
        <Authenticated path="/access" loggedIn={loggedIn} />
        <Authenticated path="/frontpage" loggedIn={loggedIn} />
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  )
}
